Response: { "instance_id": "i-w7x8y9z0", "state": "running", "message": "Instance i-w7x8y9z0 successfully started in eu-west-3." }

Question: Shut off the legacy API gateway i-a0b1c2d3 by stopping it in ca-central-1.
Call: { "func_call": "stop_instance", "instance_id": "i-a0b1c2d3", "region": "ca-central-1" }
